From c5b062e5248ebdfeecf5cb3bf96d4302c278bd3d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Yifei Sun <ysun@hey.com>
Date: Thu, 26 Mar 2026 14:31:03 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 1/1] ssh: run activation in detached systemd unit

in switch/test goals, activation is now launched
via systemd-run as a transient unit and polled
via systemctl show

this allows activation to complete even when ssh
drops during network/firewall restarts
---
